body:
`knnBeta` has the following syntax:

```json
{
  $search: {
    "index": "<index name>", // optional, defaults to "default"
    "knnBeta": {
      "vector": [<array-of-numbers>],
      "path": "<field-to-search>",
      "filter": {<filter-specification>},
      "k": <number>,
      "score": {<options>}
    }
  }
}
```
